title: Boil Water Notice – Information for Residents of High Country (Wondecla) (Tablelands Regional Council)
text: ( Source : Tablelands Regional Council ) Your property is on an untreated water supply against which we have returned a positive E.coli reading in our routine monitoring. In response we are issuing a boil water alert for your household.
